<div class="article">
	<h1>                                                 夏日度假去那好</h1>
	<div>
		<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;随着夏季的到来，生活在快节奏的都市人群，更显酷热烦闷，周末出游避暑已成为生活中一重要环节。秦岭山脉有许多农家乐去那里好呢？ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 今天我为大家推荐一个度假纳凉的好地方，西安清风山寨农家乐：清风山寨位于汤峪湖森林公园内，离西安40公里；离汤峪温泉2公里；这里山清水秀环境优美，清风山寨座落在汤峪湖西峰山半山腰，依山傍水，风格古朴清雅，整个山寨都在密林中，可同时容纳180人就餐，寨内有20个娱乐项目，都修建在原始密林内，您在娱乐时就能感受到浓浓的清凉和大自然的神奇。无论您坐在山寨的那个角落，都能吹到清凉的山风欣赏到碧绿的湖水秀美的大山，在这里度假就是一种享受。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; ">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img width="500" height="375" alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110620/866507ae8f7c0459ad8096723da957f7.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 清风山寨的 一角 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 清风山寨从去年4月分开业以来，接待了大量的团队和散客，大家对清风山寨的环境风格服务菜品给出了高度的评价和表扬，来清风山寨大的团队有；西安聚志公司；西安雨花西餐厅；西安唐华宾馆；东大街乔丹专卖；奥林巴斯公司；西安工交三公司；陕西省印刷厂；咸阳快捷酒店；曲江龙湖物业；西安华山锻造厂；西京医院；西安拥有软件；北京中聚物流；西安良子公司；西安劳动局；陕北青苹果旅行社；西安百度公司；西安交大；西安外事；长安师范大学；西安金源电器等等～～～您想感受清凉的假如生活，就来清风山寨吧。</p><p style="text-align: center; ">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;qing &nbsp;<img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110620/26a8b09e135d1f55819513d0b8d79705.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; ">清风山寨大门</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img width="500" height="375" alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110620/86fe6b2a27278a50a2cb101b34b1e8b6.jpg" /></p><p style="text-align: center; ">清风山寨的一角</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110620/488d9738d6c4a1548c62bec0d4b04250.jpg" /></p><p style="text-align: center; ">清风山寨烧烤去</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110620/bbd0d1c6fcebf951b34214eb37a7784e.jpg" /></p><p style="text-align: center; ">清风山寨情侣专区</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110620/4930809a87c4105fa2ca53f9a63cb6da.jpg" /></p><p style="text-align: center; ">清风山寨门头</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110620/fac2ba749616a75ba2811d1d8195850f.jpg" /></p><p style="text-align: center; ">清风山寨大院</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110620/5e014e8973db4e5188decec6bda01138.jpg" /></p><p style="text-align: center; ">清风山寨娱乐区一角</p><p style="text-align: center; ">本文引用www.qingfengshanzhai.com</p><p style="text-align: center; ">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; ">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
